<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-10-10T18:05:01-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-10-10T18:05:01-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-10T18:05:01-04:00</updated><title> Google Meet 增加了对 1080p 群组视频通话的支持</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 多色“G”徽标的插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/IQHJoHMm2Z-bIGbDynJE0sIEE00=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72742350/STK093_Google_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;NdjJN3&quot;>;Google 正在启用以下功能：&lt; a href=&quot;https://workspaceupdates.googleblog.com/2023/10/full-hd-resolution-for-group-meetings-google-meet.html&quot;>;在群组通话期间流式传输 1080p 质量的网络摄像头视频&lt;/a>;对于工作区订阅者。该公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/4/26/23699733/google-meet-1080p-video-calls-hd&quot;>;首次启用&lt;/a>;高品质视频功能四月回来；然而，当时它只在一对一的会议中起作用。现在，该功能已扩展到包含三名或更多参与者的网络群组通话。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;BLsUuc&quot;>;要选择使用新功能，拥有全高清（或更好）网络摄像头的参与者将需要通过接受自动出现在加入屏幕上的提示来打开它。启用后，视频框右上角会出现 1080p 图标，以确认其已打开。如果启用的用户被固定或者观看者有足够大的屏幕，会议中的人员可以观看更高质量的视频...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2023/10/10/23911773/google-meet-workspace-1080p-full-hd-group-video-calls&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911773/google-meet-workspace-1080p-full-hd-group-video-calls" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/10/23911773/google-meet-workspace-1080p-full-hd-group-video-calls</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-10T17:58:06-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-10T17:58:06-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊设备上 10 月 Prime 会员日最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>;